								<p class="author"><strong><a href="http://www.rackaid.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Jeff H</a></strong> &middot; 08/30/2010 10:44 am</p>
								<blockquote>
									<p>What is being shown with screen&#8212;list?<br />
If it is listed as attached, you can use:</p>

<p>screen -x -R</p>

<p>and it will force detach the screen.&nbsp; If it is listed as dead, the socket is no longer active and it cannot be recovered.
</p>
